<p><strong><em>Spider Climb.</em></strong> The steeder can climb difficult surfaces, including upside down on ceilings, without needing to make an ability check.</p>

<p><strong><em>Leap.</em></strong> The steeder can expend all its movement on its turn to jump up to 60 feet vertically or horizontally, provided that is speed is at least 30 feet.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. Hit: 7 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage, and the target must make a DC 12 Constitution saving throw, taking 4 (1d8) acid damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>

